video.title: Grizzy and the Lemmings
video.synopsis: Strong, whip-smart Grizzy rules a Canadian forest, where he has his paws full with a family of frolicsome lemmings.

episodes.title: Never Judge A Bear By Its Cover

episodes.synopsis: When an unbearable heat wave hits Nutty Hill, Grizzy takes refuge in a refrigerator full of Lemmings.
episodes.title: Polar Bear

episodes.synopsis: As Grizzy goes to prep for a bear-sized feast, he discovers the Lemmings have used his delicious ingredients for another food affair.
episodes.title: Bear Spread

episodes.synopsis: When the ranger's smartphone grabs Grizzy's undivided attention, the Lemmings work to regain access to its music app.
episodes.title: Cellular Bear

episodes.synopsis: After a mysterious egg hatches at Grizzy's front door, he struggles to tolerate the newest addition to the Lemmings squad.
episodes.title: Jurassic Bear

episodes.synopsis: Before Grizzy can impress a she-bear by slimming down, he must first kick the Lemmings off the workout machines they use as an amusement park.
episodes.title: Extreme Fitness

episodes.synopsis: A bumper car or a back massager? Grizzy and the Lemmings fight over the ranger's new robot vacuum cleaner.
episodes.title: Domestic Robots

episodes.synopsis: With one high-tech remote, Grizzy controls the entire cabin. But with great power to rid himself of the Lemmings comes the chance for things to go awry.
episodes.title: Mass Control

episodes.synopsis: For the love of Grizzy's beloved chocolate spread, the Lemmings try their best to break open the fridge without waking him up.
episodes.title: Bear Under Control

episodes.synopsis: When Grizzy invites his lady-bear friend over for a buttery snack, he must first wrestle with the Lemmings for the kernels.
episodes.title: Popcorn Party

episodes.synopsis: Competition for the ranger's boombox heats up when Grizzy plots to use it for salsa dance lessons and the Lemmings have, well, other plans.
episodes.title: Dancing with the Bears

episodes.synopsis: Grizzy undergoes an identity crisis after a run-in with a metal pan. Can the Lemmings help him get back to normal?
episodes.title: Role Change

episodes.synopsis: Grizzy just wants a nap! But his claim to the couch becomes a battle of wills with the ultra-hyper Lemmings after they discover its bouncy ability.
episodes.title: Lemming Tonic

episodes.synopsis: The cabin is infested with fleas, and Grizzy's efforts to rid his home of the pesky parasites come to a pause when the Lemmings refuse to be treated.
episodes.title: Bear Itch

episodes.synopsis: When a second heat wave hits Nutty Hill, the Lemmings use the last sources of water for their pool while Grizzy tries to quench his thirst.
episodes.title: Thirst Quencher

episodes.synopsis: Grizzy's fear of spiders -- and even more so the Lemmings' use of its web for bungee jumping -- complicates his ability to kill one.
episodes.title: Spider Lemmings

episodes.synopsis: When a giant Yummy jar is the grand prize in a competition, Grizzy and the Lemmings fight to win the jackpot.
episodes.title: Random Bear

episodes.synopsis: As Grizzy relaxes in front of the TV, he discovers the Lemmings' latest mischief is causing major static.
episodes.title: Lemming Interference

episodes.synopsis: After Grizzy causes a power outage, the hard-partying Lemmings search for another energy source to continue their rave.
episodes.title: High Voltage Bear Attack

episodes.synopsis: To please his beloved she-bear, Grizzy brings her flowers. But will the delightful smell be eclipsed by the Lemmings' dung pit-diving endeavors?
episodes.title: Bear Scents

episodes.synopsis: After a terrible day filled with embarrassment and frustration, Grizzy finds a four-leaf clover that could turn his luck around.
episodes.title: Bear Luck

episodes.synopsis: As the Lemmings trick Grizzy with a powerful magnet, he uses their shenanigans to impress his beloved she-bear.
episodes.title: Magnetic Bear

episodes.synopsis: Grizzy sparks a fairy-tale frenzy when he's convinced his she-bear turned into a frog. But the Lemmings have other plans for their new croaking friend.
episodes.title: Bear Charm

episodes.synopsis: When Grizzy adopts a baby raccoon, it's up to him to protect the tiny creature from the Lemmings' dangerous games.
episodes.title: Bear's Best Friend

episodes.synopsis: When Grizzy discovers the ranger's racing video game, the Lemmings try everything to get their hands on the joystick.
episodes.title: Super Grizzy Bros.

episodes.synopsis: As Grizzy prepares a popcorn party for his love, he creates a lookalike robot to distract the Lemmings from ruining his fun.
episodes.title: Fake Brothers

episodes.synopsis: When the she-bear thinks she's a Lemming, Grizzy must fight with his little roommates in order to knock their new playmate back to her senses.
episodes.title: Mind in a Whirl

episodes.synopsis: A berry-filled meteorite causes a partridge to grow bigger. And while it's a dream for the Lemmings, for Grizzy, the giant bird is a nightmare.
episodes.title: A Sizeable Problem

episodes.synopsis: When an underground maze reveals a hidden treasure map, Grizzy and the Lemmings are motivated to find the delicious riches.
episodes.title: Treasure Bear

episodes.synopsis: An ancient scepter turns the Lemmings into Grizzy's faithful servants. It will take one lone Lemming to reverse the spell.
episodes.title: In the Service of His Majesty

episodes.synopsis: As Grizzy tries to make a wood sculpture for the she-bear, the Lemmings gnaw at the work of art to create a slide.
episodes.title: Bear Art

episodes.synopsis: When the Lemmings throw a surprise birthday party for one of their own, Grizzy's only mission is to stop the festivities.
episodes.title: Happy Birthday Lemmings!

episodes.synopsis: The she-bear loses her hair flower to a gust of wind, and Grizzy tries to retrieve it. But the Lemmings want the precious bloom for a separate scheme.
episodes.title: Flower Power

episodes.synopsis: A pair of magical Native American vases fascinate Grizzy. But just wait until the mischievous Lemmings discover the enchanted pots.
episodes.title: Teleportation's the Way to Go!

episodes.synopsis: When Grizzy finds a vintage, time-rewinding stopwatch, he finally gains an advantage over the Lemmings. Temporarily.
episodes.title: Bear Countdown

episodes.synopsis: Another day of TV watching and relaxing is interrupted by the Lemmings. This time, their mischief includes hot-air balloons and a helium tank.
episodes.title: Lemmings Airlines

episodes.synopsis: The ranger's new cozy recliner is the ultimate relaxation for Grizzy -- if only the Lemmings don't transform it into their own multipurpose playground.
episodes.title: Relax Bear

episodes.synopsis: After the she-bear watches the Lemmings kitesurf, Grizzy tries to outdo them with his own DIY aircraft.
episodes.title: Bear Gliding

episodes.synopsis: When the Lemmings realize that the shrill sounds of a flute paralyze Grizzy, they use the tunes to steal Yummy chocolate spread.
episodes.title: The Sound of a Lemming

episodes.synopsis: As Grizzy settles in to watch his favorite TV documentary, the Lemmings gain access to a windpump, a TV antenna and the roof, where trouble ensues.
episodes.title: Bear in the Wind

episodes.synopsis: When Grizzy notices the she-bear is impressed by the construction of building blocks, he becomes determined to erect a colossal structure.
episodes.title: Construction Bear

episodes.synopsis: When the Lemmings become masters in martial arts, Grizzy reads up on the craft in order to become a pro and fight back.
episodes.title: Kung Fu Lemmings

episodes.synopsis: The Lemmings throw a loud fiesta as Grizzy tries to return to a dream where he's a valiant knight.
episodes.title: A Midsummer Bear's Dream

episodes.synopsis: When the Yummy supply runs out, Grizzy believes he can follow its complicated recipe to make more of the tasty spread.
episodes.title: Manufacturing Secret

episodes.synopsis: Grizzy panics when he loses the diamond in the ranger's engagement ring and realizes the Lemmings are using it for a spinning-top contest.
episodes.title: Bling Bling Bear

episodes.synopsis: After a computer zaps him into a highly intelligent bear, Grizzy plans to use his new IQ to get rid of the Lemmings.
episodes.title: Intellectual Bear

episodes.synopsis: Grizzy unwittingly foils the Lemmings' plans for an afternoon snack made with the last jar of chocolate spread.
episodes.title: Voodoo Blanket

episodes.synopsis: Using the ranger's new equipment, Grizzy tries to print a selfie. But the Lemmings' newfound obsession with paper airplanes causes a hiccup.
episodes.title: Bear Prints

episodes.synopsis: In a rare moment of working together, Grizzy and the Lemmings team to investigate the disappearance of a crate full of their favorite delicious treat.
episodes.title: Inspector Grizzy

episodes.synopsis: When the Lemmings barricade themselves in the cabin to throw a party, Grizzy doesn't wait for an invitation to gain access.
episodes.title: No Entrance!

episodes.synopsis: A sip of soda and a pack of magic white beans turn the Lemmings into a band of bouncing fur balls, disrupting Grizzy's naptime.
episodes.title: Lemmings Indigestion

episodes.synopsis: In an attempt to thrill his beloved she-bear, Grizzy decides to learn Beethoven's "Fr Elise" on an old piano before he tosses it out.
episodes.title: Sonata in Bear Major

episodes.synopsis: When the Lemmings discover a mysterious laser beam that miniaturizes and multiplies objects, they chase down Grizzy to try it on him.
episodes.title: Bear Fractions

episodes.synopsis: Grizzy and the Lemmings fight over an egg-dropping slot machine that houses prizes they've dreamed of, including a rocket and costume jewelry.
episodes.title: The Bear that Laid Golden Eggs

episodes.synopsis: Grizzy uses the ranger's new gadget to become a smarter bear. But first, he wants to learn how to get rid of his obnoxious houseguests.
episodes.title: Crash Training Course

episodes.synopsis: When Grizzy and the Lemmings find an old box stuck on a branch on the side of a cliff, they recall the first time they met as kids.
episodes.title: As Far as Bear Can Remember

episodes.synopsis: The Lemmings find a new chemistry set to occupy themselves. But when their experimenting interferes with Grizzy's TV time, they must be stopped.
episodes.title: Chemical Lemmings

episodes.synopsis: After his TV remote is stolen by a thieving partridge, Grizzy taps the Lemmings to urgently recover his high-tech possession.
episodes.title: Remote Control

episodes.synopsis: Grizzy and the Lemmings chase butterflies for different reasons -- he for a romantic gift for his love, they for a game of Helicopter.
episodes.title: The Bear and the Butterfly

episodes.synopsis: A fight over a pair of running shoes intensifies when Grizzy discovers their comfort and the Lemmings become addicted to how well they bounce.
episodes.title: Get Off My Tennis Shoes

episodes.synopsis: When Grizzy babysits for his crushs cub, the Lemmings decide to pump the youngster full of soda for burps and giggles.
episodes.title: Babysitting

episodes.synopsis: When Grizzy locks his food in a burglar-proof safe, the Lemmings make every ridiculous attempt to unlock the goods.
episodes.title: Bear Under Lock and Key

episodes.synopsis: After witnessing a magician turn a partridge into a bouquet of flowers, Grizzy teaches himself magic in the hopes of making the Lemmings disappear.
episodes.title: Lemming Blues

episodes.synopsis: On a sweltering day, Grizzy's ice cream cravings turn cold when he realizes the Lemmings ate all of the chilly dessert.
episodes.title: Snow Lemmings

episodes.synopsis: The Lemmings get hooked on a virtual reality game, and Grizzy follows suit in his addiction to a salmon fishing app.
episodes.title: Augmented Bear

episodes.synopsis: Nothing comes between Grizzy and his salmon -- except a block of ice. To thaw his meal, he'll have to swipe the blow dryer from the Lemmings.
episodes.title: Lemmings Under Pressure

episodes.synopsis: The Lemmings' dream to reach the stars may come true after they find fireworks that could blast them into space -- but would interrupt Grizzy's nap.
episodes.title: Lemmings in Space

episodes.synopsis: As the Lemmings savor the last jar of Yummy chocolate spread undetected, Grizzy trains an adorable raccoon to sniff out the sweet concoction.
episodes.title: Sniffer Raccoon

episodes.synopsis: Leave the couch? No way. Grizzy masters his laziness with the help of the Lemmings' radio-controlled robot, which he's turned into his personal butler.
episodes.title: Transformational Bear

episodes.synopsis: Grizzy's snoring makes for good vibrations that the Lemmings can bounce to. But the tiny critters must get creative when the bear suddenly stops.
episodes.title: Shaken-Up Bear

episodes.synopsis: The ranger's birthday piata doubles as target practice for Grizzy and a fun swing for the Lemmings. The race is on to see who gets to control it.
episodes.title: Piata Party

episodes.synopsis: When Grizzy and the Lemmings discover a magical game, they're transported into the board, where each adventure comes to life.
episodes.title: Bear Game

episodes.synopsis: Realizing the Lemmings will obey a big furry puppet, Grizzy uses their gullibility to his advantage.
episodes.title: Ranger Lemming

episodes.synopsis: As the Lemmings use leftover marshmallows as a trampoline, an unimpressed Grizzy changes his tune when he eats one of the pillowy confections.
episodes.title: Halloween Bear

episodes.synopsis: Grizzy needs to scrub up before offering a gift to his crush, but there's one problem: The Lemmings are hogging the soap for their bobsled.
episodes.title: Clean Bear

episodes.synopsis: Thanks to a strange figurine, Grizzy swaps spirits with a moose. To switch back, he must steal the figurine from the pesky Lemmings, who've stolen it.
episodes.title: Wandering Spirits

episodes.synopsis: When Grizzy finds an old hand mirror fit for a princess, he's teleported into the utopia found only in his dreams.
episodes.title: Mirror, Mirror on the Wall

episodes.synopsis: When the Lemmings discover a magic stick that brings objects to life, Grizzy plots to steal it to make his life easier.
episodes.title: Grizzy the Wizard

episodes.synopsis: One small step for the Lemmings is one giant leap for Grizzy. When fireworks explode at the cabin, all the creatures take a trip to the moon.
episodes.title: Moonwalk Bear
